6 An Act relating to crimes and punishments; amending
21 O.S. 2021, Sections 1902 and 1903, which relate to
7 the Bus Passenger Safety Act; modifying scope of
certain definitions; adding definitions; expanding
8 scope of unlawful acts; updating statutory language
and references; and declaring an emergency.
