11 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
12 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 21 O.S. 2021, Section 1902, is
13 amended to read as follows:
14 Section 1902. As used in the Bus Passenger Safety Act:
15 1. “Bus” means a vehicle designed to carry passengers that is
16 part of a network of passenger vehicles for use by the public,
17 running on a regular schedule of routes, times, and fares;
18 2. “Bus transportation company” or “company” means any person
19 or governmental entity providing for-hire transport to passengers or
20 cargo by bus rolling stock transit vehicles upon the roads, streets,
21 highways, public or dedicated rights-of-way, and turnpikes of this
22 state;
23 3. “Deadly or dangerous weapon” includes all weapons listed in
24 Section 1287 of this title, and any other weapon capable of
